00:30:26,688 --> 00:30:27,689
huwag.

491
00:30:28,022 --> 00:30:29,023
ha?

492
00:30:30,233 --> 00:30:31,776
Huwag kang maawa sa akin.

493
00:30:32,569 --> 00:30:33,778
I deserve this.

494
00:30:35,352 --> 00:30:37,057
- Ngunit...
- Ang ginawa ko

495
00:30:38,324 --> 00:30:39,505
ay hindi katanggap-tanggap.

496
00:30:40,243 --> 00:30:41,411
alam ko yun.

497
00:30:44,497 --> 00:30:45,665
Jay-jay...

498
00:30:50,670 --> 00:30:51,838
Sorry talaga.

499
00:30:55,091 --> 00:30:56,676
hindi ko alam kung bakit
Ginawa ko ang ginawa ko.

500
00:30:58,177 --> 00:31:00,555
Hindi ko alam, something
lumapit sa akin at...

501
00:31:01,681 --> 00:31:03,016
hindi lang ako.

502
00:31:06,644 --> 00:31:08,104
Na-brokenhearted ako dahil…

503
00:31:09,814 --> 00:31:11,274
Dahil tinanggihan mo ako at...

504
00:31:15,820 --> 00:31:17,363
Ito ay mga hangal na palusot lamang,

505
00:31:17,666 --> 00:31:19,223
hindi nito excuse ang ginawa ko.

506
00:31:23,036 --> 00:31:24,454
Patawarin mo ako, Jay-jay.

507
00:31:29,876 --> 00:31:31,461
Tinanggap ang paghingi ng tawad.

508
00:31:34,213 --> 00:31:35,214
talaga?

509
00:31:37,842 --> 00:31:41,679
Huwag mo na lang ulitin, Kiko.

510
00:31:50,406 --> 00:31:51,820
Ako lang.

511
00:31:52,482 --> 00:31:53,984
Maaari mong ihinto ang pagtingin sa paligid.

512
00:31:59,822 --> 00:32:03,534
[pag-buzz ng telepono]

513
00:32:07,185 --> 00:32:09,025
Kaya mga kaklase mo
hinahanap na kita?

514
00:32:10,875 --> 00:32:12,777
Hindi. Hayaan mo sila.

515
00:32:15,964 --> 00:32:17,632
Alam mo ikaw
Ang swerte talaga ni Jay.

516
00:32:19,217 --> 00:32:22,053
Ang iyong mga kaibigan,
mga kaklase mo sila...

517
00:32:22,595 --> 00:32:24,055
may pakialam sila sayo.

518
00:32:26,590 --> 00:32:28,675
So much, sila na
handang ipaglaban ka.

519
00:32:34,649 --> 00:32:36,109
Hindi sila
ganyan kay Ella.

520
00:32:41,155 --> 00:32:42,674
kamusta ka dito?

521
00:32:42,799 --> 00:32:44,463
Kailan ka madidischarge?

522
00:32:46,911 --> 00:32:48,079
Mga isang buwan.

523
00:32:49,330 --> 00:32:50,331
Pero uhm,

524
00:32:50,847 --> 00:32:54,351
sabi nila mga anim hanggang walo
buwan para sa aking ganap na paggaling.

525
00:32:55,712 --> 00:32:58,756
At pagkatapos ay kailangan ko
sumailalim sa physical therapy.

526
00:32:59,632 --> 00:33:01,011
Paano ang pag-aaral mo?

527
00:33:03,177 --> 00:33:04,637
Na-expel ako, Jay.

528
00:33:05,138 --> 00:33:06,139
Tandaan?

529
00:33:08,901 --> 00:33:11,070
Ano nga pala ang sinabi ni Freya?

530
00:33:15,520 --> 00:33:16,524
wala.

531
00:33:16,524 --> 00:33:18,317
I mean naghiwalay kami kaya...

532
00:33:18,958 --> 00:33:20,876
sabi niya ayaw niya
isang lalaking may kapansanan.

533
00:33:23,698 --> 00:33:25,783
Bagay talaga yung babaeng yun.

534
00:33:26,701 --> 00:33:29,495
Well ang ibig kong sabihin,
ganyan lang siya.

535
00:33:31,164 --> 00:33:32,498
Kapag wala ka nang pakinabang sa kanya,

536
00:33:32,523 --> 00:33:34,859
binitawan ka lang niya
parang mainit na patatas.

537
00:33:35,752 --> 00:33:36,753
nakikita ko yun.

538
00:33:41,257 --> 00:33:42,967
Hindi siya palagi
ganoon din.

539
00:33:44,177 --> 00:33:47,007
Naalala ko siya noon
mabait talaga kami ni Mykel.

540
00:33:47,680 --> 00:33:49,891
Noong bata pa tayo
at sa panahon ng summer classes.

541
00:33:52,268 --> 00:33:54,145
Kamakailan lang talaga
na nagbago siya.

542
00:33:56,022 --> 00:33:57,690
Anong nangyari sa kanya?

543
00:34:03,780 --> 00:34:05,031
Tanong ni Keifer at Yuri.

544
00:34:05,573 --> 00:34:06,574
ha?

545
00:34:07,492 --> 00:34:08,910
Sa naalala ko,

546
00:34:11,120 --> 00:34:14,499
Si Freya, nang mamatay ang kanyang kasintahan,

547
00:34:14,524 --> 00:34:15,525
at pagkatapos,

548
00:34:16,000 --> 00:34:17,210
pagkatapos...

549
00:34:17,776 --> 00:34:21,738
napadaan siya
Keifer, Yuri, at Aries.

550
00:34:34,049 --> 00:34:35,707
Nandiyan si Jay.

551
00:34:38,940 --> 00:34:40,274
saan ka napunta?

552
00:34:41,651 --> 00:34:42,860
Late ako nagising!

553
00:34:42,975 --> 00:34:44,656
Sabi ni Ci-N may pinuntahan ka daw.

554
00:34:48,023 --> 00:34:50,400
Oo! Kaya naman natagalan ako.

555
00:34:50,830 --> 00:34:52,790
Bakit hindi mo sinasagot ang iyong telepono?

556
00:34:53,281 --> 00:34:54,282
Uhm...

557
00:34:55,623 --> 00:34:57,583
Dahil alam kong ikaw ang tumatawag.

558
00:34:57,857 --> 00:35:00,144
Sa susunod sabihin mo sa akin
kung may pupuntahan ka.

559
00:35:00,227 --> 00:35:01,520
Kaya wala tayong dapat ikabahala.

560
00:35:02,135 --> 00:35:04,346
Paano kung ang pangyayari
kay Rory na naman ang mangyayari?

561
00:35:06,689 --> 00:35:07,690
Sorry..

562
00:35:08,709 --> 00:35:10,794
Promise next time, sasabihin ko sayo.

563
00:35:12,388 --> 00:35:13,388
Lahat kayo.

564
00:35:14,008 --> 00:35:15,602
I wonder anong meron?

565
00:35:16,561 --> 00:35:18,187
Tiningnan ko lang silang dalawa,

566
00:35:18,248 --> 00:35:20,333
pero parang nanonood si Josh.

567
00:35:23,989 --> 00:35:25,407
Umalis ka dyan, uupo ako.

568
00:35:26,487 --> 00:35:27,488
umalis ka na!

569
00:35:37,874 --> 00:35:39,542
I wonder kung anong nangyari kay Freya

570
00:35:39,567 --> 00:35:41,438
na siya ay natapos
kay Keifer at Yuri?

571
00:35:42,036 --> 00:35:43,412
Tapos si Aries din?

572
00:35:43,846 --> 00:35:45,378
Ah, tama.

573
00:35:45,406 --> 00:35:47,894
May sinabi sa akin si Rakki kanina.

574
00:35:48,229 --> 00:35:50,940
Na may something
between Aries and Freya before.

575
00:35:51,162 --> 00:35:53,138
Baka yun ang ibig sabihin ni Kiko?

576
00:35:53,275 --> 00:35:55,053
At ngayon, si Edrix din?

577
00:35:58,519 --> 00:35:59,520
Bakit?

578
00:36:00,146 --> 00:36:01,147
wala.

579
00:36:26,939 --> 00:36:28,065
Pagkain, pagkain, pagkain!

580
00:36:28,090 --> 00:36:29,091
Mga bata!

581
00:36:29,116 --> 00:36:30,693
Hindi ka dapat maging mapili!

582
00:36:30,718 --> 00:36:33,232
Walang sinuman ang may karapatan!
Wala ni isa sa inyo ang nag-ambag.

583
00:36:33,700 --> 00:36:35,035
Kumain ng mabuti.

584
00:36:35,313 --> 00:36:36,313
Ayan na tayo!

585
00:36:38,309 --> 00:36:39,310
At galit ka?

586
00:36:39,335 --> 00:36:40,573
Nakuha na kita, bro.

587
00:36:44,357 --> 00:36:45,358
Ci!

588
00:36:45,980 --> 00:36:46,980
Sumama ka sa akin.

589
00:36:47,763 --> 00:36:49,443
By the way Jay,
kamusta ang iyong maliit na gawain?

590
00:36:49,630 --> 00:36:50,966
Paano na si Kiko?

591
00:36:51,576 --> 00:36:52,576
Masyado kang maingay!

592
00:36:53,012 --> 00:36:54,221
Napakadrama!

593
00:36:54,246 --> 00:36:55,926
Ano ang ibig mong sabihing dramatic?
Masyado kang maingay.

594
00:36:56,675 --> 00:36:58,340
talaga? wag ka
may kahihiyan ba

595
00:36:58,417 --> 00:37:00,337
Pina-check up mo yung lalaki
matalo ka sa isang pulpol!

596
00:37:01,674 --> 00:37:03,006
tanong ko lang.

597
00:37:03,914 --> 00:37:06,167
Hindi siya mukhang maganda.

598
00:37:06,986 --> 00:37:09,697
Siya ay may kapansanan at
hindi siya makagalaw ng maayos.

599
00:37:09,722 --> 00:37:10,723
Parang ganito siya.

600
00:37:10,748 --> 00:37:11,821
Ahh.

601
00:37:13,547 --> 00:37:14,548
Sayang naman.

602
00:37:15,098 --> 00:37:16,433
Ano ang ibig mong sabihin masyadong masama? Bobo!

603
00:37:16,458 --> 00:37:17,542
Ah! Ang sakit, Jay!

604
00:37:17,567 --> 00:37:18,746
Masakit!

605
00:37:19,555 --> 00:37:20,681
Ano ang pinagsasabi mo?

606
00:37:20,706 --> 00:37:22,413
- Wala akong sinasabi.
- Baliw ka.

607
00:37:22,849 --> 00:37:24,142
Isusumbong kita kay Keifer!

608
00:37:24,330 --> 00:37:26,582
Doon ka magaling,
iulat kay Keifer—

609
00:37:26,607 --> 00:37:28,067
Keifer, si Jay-jay ay gumagamit ng kabastusan–

610
00:37:28,567 --> 00:37:29,735
Halika dito!

611
00:37:29,735 --> 00:37:30,735
Halika dito!

612
00:37:31,070 --> 00:37:32,449
Lalabas tayo!

613
00:37:32,474 --> 00:37:33,531
Pero ang init!

614
00:37:33,556 --> 00:37:35,180
Lalabas tayo, bye.

615
00:37:37,677 --> 00:37:39,303
Halika dito. Ikaw ay
sobrang ingay simula kanina!

616
00:37:39,328 --> 00:37:41,049
Wala akong sinabi
tungkol sa paglabas.

617
00:37:41,074 --> 00:37:42,623
Ano tayo
gagawin sa labas?

618
00:37:42,623 --> 00:37:43,666
Ang init, Jay-jay!

619
00:37:43,842 --> 00:37:45,135
Ang sakit mo talaga!

620
00:37:45,793 --> 00:37:47,503
Iparinig ito sa Section E!

621
00:37:47,962 --> 00:37:49,422
Dadalhin mo ako sa gulo!

622
00:37:49,647 --> 00:37:51,607
Nakakainis ka.
nagugutom pa ako.

623
00:37:51,632 --> 00:37:52,820
ako rin.

624
00:37:53,259 --> 00:37:54,552
Kasalanan mo ito!

625
00:37:55,052 --> 00:37:56,929
At least kumakain ang pusa.

626
00:37:58,723 --> 00:37:59,515
ang cute!

627
00:37:59,515 --> 00:38:00,850
Sinabi ko lang na walang tao
dapat marinig ang tungkol dito.

628
00:38:00,850 --> 00:38:02,101
Si Josh yun!

629
00:38:02,393 --> 00:38:04,437
- Ah talaga?
- Oo! Talaga, talaga?

630
00:38:05,998 --> 00:38:06,998
Hoy, Josh!

631
00:38:07,072 --> 00:38:08,072
Oh?

632
00:38:08,541 --> 00:38:09,792
Ang cute ng pusa!

633
00:38:09,817 --> 00:38:11,152
Anong himala.

634
00:38:11,738 --> 00:38:13,029
Namimigay ka ng pagkain...

635
00:38:13,029 --> 00:38:14,140
ngunit sa isang pusa.

636
00:38:14,828 --> 00:38:16,148
Wala lang, hindi pa ako gutom.

637
00:38:16,616 --> 00:38:17,856
Kaya binigay ko na lang sa kanya yung lunch ko.

638
00:38:18,185 --> 00:38:19,561
Dapat meron ka
binigay lang naman sa akin diba?

639
00:38:19,722 --> 00:38:21,365
- Nagugutom ka rin ba?
- Oo!

640
00:38:22,872 --> 00:38:24,932
Edy, halika na at kumain.

641
00:38:24,957 --> 00:38:25,958
Hoy, Ci-N!

642
00:38:26,584 --> 00:38:27,887
kung ako sayo,
Hindi ko gagawin iyon.

643
00:38:27,912 --> 00:38:29,288
Bakit? ito ay mainit ang ulo?

644
00:38:30,629 --> 00:38:32,340
Masyado kang kumain, Edy.

645
00:38:32,590 --> 00:38:33,591
Sinong tinatawag mong Edy?

646
00:38:34,525 --> 00:38:35,526
Ang pusa.

647
00:38:35,811 --> 00:38:37,587
ha? Hindi yan si Edy.

648
00:38:37,636 --> 00:38:38,637
Sino siya?

649
00:38:38,839 --> 00:38:40,341
wala. Wala siyang pangalan.

650
00:38:40,714 --> 00:38:41,714
Tapos siya si Edy.

651
00:38:42,444 --> 00:38:43,987
Saan mo nakuha si Edy?

652
00:38:44,477 --> 00:38:45,478
Ang kanyang kulay.

653
00:38:46,273 --> 00:38:48,441
Yung galing
ang komersyal na baterya.

654
00:38:48,814 --> 00:38:50,900
- Kaya Edy.
- Ah tama!

655
00:38:50,925 --> 00:38:53,344
Itim na pusa din yan!

656
00:38:53,652 --> 00:38:54,653
Napakatalino mo!

657
00:38:54,678 --> 00:38:57,235
Dapat matalino rin ang mga kaibigan mo.

658
00:38:57,406 --> 00:38:58,866
Hindi si Edy yan!

659
00:38:59,750 --> 00:39:01,410
- Kahit ano.
- Saan ka pupunta?

660
00:39:01,410 --> 00:39:03,771
- Kukuha ako ng pagkain para kay Edy.
- Ay, Jay!

661
00:39:04,582 --> 00:39:05,582
Bakit?

662
00:39:07,416 --> 00:39:08,876
Kilala mo naman sila diba?

663
00:39:09,622 --> 00:39:10,622
ha?

664
00:39:11,194 --> 00:39:12,194
WHO?

665
00:39:12,505 --> 00:39:15,758
Ang mga nakita mo sa
ang gabi ng pista.

666
00:39:22,856 --> 00:39:24,190
Ah...

667
00:39:25,851 --> 00:39:26,852
Oh?

668
00:39:29,021 --> 00:39:31,607
Kung meron man
sa pagitan mo at ni Keifer,

669
00:39:31,982 --> 00:39:35,528
ipangako mo sa akin na hinding-hindi
sabihin sa kanya ang tungkol dito.

670
00:39:36,217 --> 00:39:38,011
"Something between us," talaga?

671
00:39:39,412 --> 00:39:41,414
Pero diba sabi ko sayo,

672
00:39:41,534 --> 00:39:43,202
ligtas sila ni Keifer.

673
00:39:43,494 --> 00:39:45,037
- Talaga?
- Oo!

674
00:39:45,958 --> 00:39:48,419
Alam mo naman si Keifer
kapag galit siya diba?

675
00:39:49,333 --> 00:39:53,838
Kaya habang hindi pa natin alam
ano ang magiging reaksyon ni Keifer...

676
00:39:54,296 --> 00:39:55,464
wag mo na lang sabihin sa kanya.

677
00:39:56,590 --> 00:39:59,468
Kung sakaling maayos ang lahat.

678
00:40:01,929 --> 00:40:03,556
Ano ang sinusubukan mong sabihin?

679
00:40:06,016 --> 00:40:07,418
Kaibigan ko sina Mayo at Kit.

680
00:40:08,410 --> 00:40:09,732
Gusto kong maging masaya sila.

681
00:40:10,764 --> 00:40:12,784
Pero iniisip ko,

682
00:40:13,807 --> 00:40:16,560
baka hindi na sila masaktan kung

683
00:40:16,694 --> 00:40:18,529
itigil na nila ang kabaliwan na ito.

684
00:40:19,405 --> 00:40:20,821
Sila ang naghihirap.

685
00:40:21,590 --> 00:40:22,842
Mas lalo lang silang nasasaktan

686
00:40:22,867 --> 00:40:25,077
dahil sila
hindi kayang ipagtanggol ang sarili.

687
00:40:26,495 --> 00:40:27,705
You know what, tama ka,

688
00:40:28,330 --> 00:40:29,874
Napaisip ako niyan.

689
00:40:30,198 --> 00:40:31,575
Hello Edy!

690
00:40:32,460 --> 00:40:33,961
Ito ay para sa iyo.

691
00:40:34,770 --> 00:40:36,601
Kaya ba tahimik ka,
kasi ganyan ka mag isip?

692
00:40:36,797 --> 00:40:38,132
Paano mo napansin iyon?

693
00:40:38,157 --> 00:40:39,783
Dapat ko ring gawin iyon.

694
00:40:40,443 --> 00:40:41,694
Para makapag-isip ako ng maayos.

695
00:40:41,719 --> 00:40:44,263
Ayan! Pakiramdam niya ay nahihiya siya.

696
00:40:49,226 --> 00:40:50,686
Jay, kinagat ako nito!

697
00:40:51,046 --> 00:40:53,214
Kasalanan mo 'to, bakla!

698
00:40:53,361 --> 00:40:54,597
Ayan, nahirapan ka na naman!

699
00:40:55,683 --> 00:40:58,302
Jay-jay, baka mamatay ako.
Baka may rabies siya!

700
00:40:58,903 --> 00:40:59,904
Ikaw ang may kasalanan nito Josh!

701
00:40:59,904 --> 00:41:01,030
Halika dito, titingnan ko.

702
00:41:01,030 --> 00:41:03,157
Magpabakuna kaagad,
tara, tingnan natin!

703
00:41:03,182 --> 00:41:04,925
Jay-jay, ayoko
para ma-injection!

704
00:41:04,950 --> 00:41:06,994
Napakadrama mo,
wala kang magagawa diyan!

705
00:41:06,994 --> 00:41:08,162
Magpa-inject ka, umuwi ka na!

706
00:41:08,187 --> 00:41:09,317
Puputulin nila yan,

707
00:41:09,351 --> 00:41:10,644
ikaw ay isang dakot!

708
00:41:13,323 --> 00:41:14,658
Masakit pa rin ang kagat, Jay.

709
00:41:15,002 --> 00:41:16,082
Sobrang sakit ng injection.

710
00:41:17,480 --> 00:41:22,151
Poor brat, nakikita ko ba?

711
00:41:22,176 --> 00:41:23,594
Tingnan mo, kinagat ako nito.

712
00:41:23,594 --> 00:41:25,763
- Bigyan mo ako, ipapamasahe ko.
- Masakit.

713
00:41:25,763 --> 00:41:27,973
Doon, para mawala ang sakit.

714
00:41:28,557 --> 00:41:30,851
- Ganun.
- Salamat, Jay.

715
00:41:30,876 --> 00:41:31,877
Okay na ba ngayon?

716
00:41:33,437 --> 00:41:34,939
Masyado kang attached kay Jay-jay.

717
00:41:34,964 --> 00:41:36,340
Sobra na yan.

718
00:41:42,052 --> 00:41:44,028
Nagseselos na naman yata siya.

719
00:41:53,791 --> 00:41:54,833
At itong isa pa.

720
00:41:55,334 --> 00:41:57,044
Anong gagawin ko?

721
00:41:57,503 --> 00:41:59,380
Nagseselos ba sila kay Ci-N?

722
00:42:00,589 --> 00:42:01,757
Bagay ba kayo ni Yuri?

723
00:42:03,173 --> 00:42:04,173
ha?

724
00:42:04,198 --> 00:42:05,210
Hindi!

725
00:42:05,408 --> 00:42:07,952
Oo! Bakit siya
umaarte na parang ikaw?

726
00:42:08,073 --> 00:42:09,324
Parang pag-aari ka niya.

727
00:42:10,015 --> 00:42:12,309
Jay, huwag mong sabihing oo
kung liligawan ka niya.

728
00:42:12,842 --> 00:42:15,203
- Baka—
- Parang hindi mo kilala si Yuri.

729
00:42:15,467 --> 00:42:17,147
Siya ay eksaktong pareho
way with Ella before.

730
00:42:18,228 --> 00:42:19,228
Ay, oo.

731
00:42:20,776 --> 00:42:22,403
Oo...

732
00:42:25,896 --> 00:42:27,230
iihi lang ako, okay?

733
00:42:34,248 --> 00:42:35,249
Hoy, Kit!

734
00:42:35,916 --> 00:42:36,917
